Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.20,0:00:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.08,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.82,0:00:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.27,0:00:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.25,0:01:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.33,0:01:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.37,0:01:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.61,0:01:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.96,0:01:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.13,0:01:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.90,0:01:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在春天來臨之前\N我都會是一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.92,0:02:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員真的那麼說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.89,0:02:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,在我面前說得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.43,0:02:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她沒有說出你的名字吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.43,0:02:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定她指的是三鷹教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,這是不可能的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.77,0:02:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝各位的搭乘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.94,0:02:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是神田,神田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.81,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下車囉,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.74,0:02:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.95,0:02:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神田,神田到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.71,0:02:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下車的旅客優先\N請在兩旁耐心等候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要下車,我要下車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借過一下,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好險…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.27,0:03:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#77五代幹得好!\N偶爾展現男子氣概
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.64,0:03:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳怎麼啦\N怎麼連午飯也不吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是跟公寓的寡婦\N出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.89,0:03:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼了?\N為了五代老師的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.49,0:03:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜對了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就說給我們聽嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.96,0:03:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師今天幹勁十足的\N出去找工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?他還沒找到工作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,八神妳不是因為這樣才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸一點都不在乎的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他到底把我當什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳離家出走就沒有效囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.61,0:03:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,可以跟心愛的五代老師\N在同一個屋簷下生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也很不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要虧我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.92,0:03:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的為了五代老師\N才離家出走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.96,0:03:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是在妳猶豫不決的這段期間\N萬一五代老師找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不就糟了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.10,0:03:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,很糟很糟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我還是希望他能被錄取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的這麼認為嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.31,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我心裡的某個角落\N也希望他不被錄取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟幫不上心愛之人的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個女人是很痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.85,0:04:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且上次的事\N我也覺得有點責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.09,0:04:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為上次介紹的公司倒閉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白八神的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大杯生啤酒來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,你決定進貿易公司啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本被三友商事內定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了婉拒花了很多心血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.14,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想說到貿易公司上班的話\N或許可以馬上被派到國外去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.21,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.58,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來大家都找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼貿易公司,派遣國外嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.46,0:05:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們連二、三流公司\N都不理我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.84,0:05:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法\N明天再繼續努力就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.21,0:05:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你因為手中握有最後的王牌\N才敢說這種風涼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王牌?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是八神這個強力的人脈關係啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了,這條線已經沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明還在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.85,0:05:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把人家的女兒\N抓來當人質,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要亂說\N別人聽到會誤會啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己跑來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.90,0:05:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想靠她的話\N我還會跟你一起出來找工作嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.16,0:06:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼還悠閒地\N在幼稚園打工?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.23,0:06:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有這種心情吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪裡悠閒了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.83,0:06:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是趁找工作的空檔\N去幼稚園打工的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.93,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟孩子們在一起\N心情會變得很輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.51,0:06:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個時候\N能忘記找工作的苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是在逃避吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃避?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.78,0:06:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆,再來一杯大杯的生啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.88,0:06:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚豁出去喝了,醉給它爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.24,0:06:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?這些鞋子是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,是管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.92,0:07:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼可以這樣,那是五代的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣正經八百的嘛\N請進,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.33,0:07:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,洗完澡先來喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,我不用…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.17,0:07:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N五代老師有沒有跟妳聯絡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.24,0:07:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說得沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然他今天也找不到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣很好啊,八神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.45,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,至少狀況\N回復到原來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.45,0:07:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代找不到工作\N對你們有什麼好處嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦,我們只是隨便說說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.43,0:07:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在八成跟阪本在藉酒澆愁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也差不多\N該幫他想想辦法了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.87,0:07:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊\N妳是為了這個才離家出走的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.67,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.08,0:08:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是八神\N妳爸爸也有他的立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太為難他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.19,0:08:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳討厭我爸\N幫五代老師找到工作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是,我只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這應該由五代來決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.53,0:08:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是八神的爸爸\N推薦個一兩人應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.70,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊\N畢竟是一流公司的人事部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神的爸爸好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託\N妳是已經了解狀況才來的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不對嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.25,0:08:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神可能是施加的壓力還不夠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,施展激烈一點的作戰\N或許會比較有效吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆跟五代老師\N住在同一個房間算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.13,0:08:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後硬是去登記結婚之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託,你們不要鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正事不關己\N就在那裡亂出餿主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.90,0:09:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,事到如今\N只能先把生米煮成熟飯了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是真的在為我擔心嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.02,0:09:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果五代昨晚沒有回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.53,0:09:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來只能靠八神她爸爸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.07,0:09:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說要當一年無業遊民…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N妳想把它剪成光頭嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.88,0:09:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,感覺蠻清爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,洗衣機的衣服應該洗好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看她也真是辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.39,0:10:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被夾在\N高中女生和就業的事之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要找五代嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊,他有來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊,跟平常沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.06,0:10:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要叫他來聽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.24,0:10:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做的積木\N真是幫了我們一個大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在變成園童們\N最喜歡玩的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.58,0:10:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,園長好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.15,0:11:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.56,0:11:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,積木很好玩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家開開心心去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.47,0:11:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請你發揮你這方面的長才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.64,0:11:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來擔任這次運動會的策劃委員呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我來當嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.94,0:11:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,比如說比賽用的道具\N還有運動會場的佈置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每年都是老樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.68,0:11:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?能不能想出讓孩子們\N開心盡興的主意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.49,0:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.99,0:11:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然你可以優先找工作沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.89,0:11:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.73,0:11:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥也要參加運動會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會參加嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然會囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.77,0:11:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想在運動會上玩什麼遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.84,0:11:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管向大哥哥拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,我要玩遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要玩丟圈圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要玩吃麵包比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,大家等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個一個慢慢說\N不然大哥哥怎麼聽得懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.34,0:12:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.85,0:12:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.90,0:12:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳終於願意回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是我的家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是家裡最舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,媽媽煮的菜也很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有伊吹在真的很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.72,0:13:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們兩個吃飯\N好像在守靈似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對,老公?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.69,0:13:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,不過沒想到\N伊吹已經會自己做飯吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.66,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也做給爸爸吃吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.56,0:13:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,改天,我吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹,要不要吃梨子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.97,0:13:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了,我得回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.47,0:13:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.97,0:13:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉,因為爸爸還沒幫\N五代老師寫介紹信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳為什麼回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.55,0:13:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟爸爸媽媽一起吃飯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.92,0:13:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.05,0:13:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我搬離一刻館\N也絕對不會給爸媽添麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不會給我添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子實在太任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.47,0:14:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那,接下來拜託媽媽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.54,0:14:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹,別走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老公,她走了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.54,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.78,0:14:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全家一起吃飯真的好開心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.96,0:14:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.96,0:14:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.56,0:14:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好晚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.87,0:14:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為園長要我接下\N運動會的策劃委員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以有很多事情要準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.44,0:14:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,策劃委員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下這種職務\N你找工作的事不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.04,0:14:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他大概在期望\N八神的爸爸會幫他寫介紹信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.41,0:14:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有想靠那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,八神呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.32,0:14:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.86,0:14:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?已經快10點了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不能打電話去她家問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去車站看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然很關心她嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.03,0:15:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.30,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個高中女生\N到這個時候還沒回來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明嫌她嫌得要命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.97,0:15:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這關係到他的就業啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有在期待這個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,不用裝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我去車站看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我回來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.35,0:15:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳到哪裡去了\N這麼晚才回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.66,0:15:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,你在為我擔心嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是回家去一趟而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳把介紹信拿到手了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.86,0:15:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,已經是時間上的問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.10,0:15:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.34,0:15:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要感謝她才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.37,0:15:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過,我沒有在期待這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來,提前慶祝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.45,0:15:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管慶祝幾次就業\N感覺還是很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.12,0:15:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託\N我又還沒真的找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼正經八百嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.09,0:16:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正遲早會找到工作的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人的好意要坦率地接受\N來吧,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.01,0:16:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.98,0:16:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.59,0:16:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.79,0:16:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運動會的討論會議\N能不能改從三點開始?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.76,0:16:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得去一趟大學的就職課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也真累啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.97,0:16:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這麼忙的話\N推掉策劃委員的工作不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我喜歡做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.58,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要當上班族嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.95,0:17:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是說一定啦\N只是其它沒什麼適合我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你來當褓父啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.75,0:17:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很適合這個工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.02,0:17:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很有責任感\N也很懂得如何掌握孩子的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,的確很適合\N明年夏天要不要去參加褓母考試?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.47,0:17:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,妳不要害\N正在找工作的人猶豫不決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.81,0:17:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這種工作\N比去公司上班好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.31,0:17:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對啊,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.01,0:17:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.68,0:18:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,要不要過來這裡喝啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.15,0:18:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,做完再喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.65,0:18:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一罐又有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.02,0:18:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,運動會就是明天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是個大好人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然掛名策劃委員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果根本是在做工嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.46,0:18:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家長們應該會送酒獎勵你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.53,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,我只要孩子們開心就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,你們都在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.78,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,這是介紹信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.19,0:19:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了?你就高興一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.83,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感動到說不出話來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,恭喜你找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.70,0:19:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信的金魚才能得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,快向八神部長道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.15,0:19:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.62,0:19:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.62,0:19:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我要把伊吹帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走,回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要,我還不要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.46,0:20:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我離家出走的時候說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.80,0:20:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要看到五代老師確實去上班了\N才要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.07,0:20:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次我選得十分慎重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能再發生倒閉的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸向妳保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.91,0:20:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N這關係到五代老師的將來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.08,0:20:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.05,0:20:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳再這樣任性下去\N爸爸真的要生氣了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.05,0:20:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.92,0:20:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個還給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.66,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,你要把伊吹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.86,0:20:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八神,妳也跟妳爸爸一起回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.27,0:20:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師,你為什麼不接受呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.30,0:20:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說,我非常渴望這封介紹信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我真的無法收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.92,0:20:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕自己會這樣隨波逐流下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就業的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要自己決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.86,0:21:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這是我自己的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.63,0:21:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你真的要把這個還給他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.04,0:21:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會後悔嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.37,0:21:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,請把這封介紹信給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.84,0:21:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是五代的好朋友,我姓阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.45,0:21:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟五代一樣\N一直為了找不到工作而苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就當作是做好事幫助人\N把這個給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.92,0:21:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.99,0:21:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.79,0:21:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為他這次\N終於找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.97,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛,就愛耍酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.57,0:21:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,八神走了還真無聊\N以後就少一個人陪我玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.41,0:21:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走,再去重頭喝過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.28,0:21:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.18,0:22:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼做是對的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.55,0:22:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.75,0:22:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得心裡的某個角落\N好像在後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.76,0:22:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,工作是一輩子的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.33,0:22:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.44,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算找到不適合自己的工作\N做起來也會很痛苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.91,0:22:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.47,0:22:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,能不能請妳來參加\N明天的運動會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.75,0:22:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.73,0:22:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.73,0:22:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.91,0:23:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.51,0:23:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只差一點點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.14,0:23:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.36,0:23:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兔女郎酒家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.79,0:23:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下每晚都能喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.09,0:23:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝個夠本吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.73,0:23:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.40,0:23:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.77,0:24:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N「這是秘密!五代的打工奮鬥記!」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.60,0:24:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去告訴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.67,0:24:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.11,0:24:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.78,0:24:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.95,0:24:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.96,0:24:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.20,0:24:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.41,0:24:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.01,0:24:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.88,0:24:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.59,0:24:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這燭火依偎著的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.86,0:25:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.74,0:25:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試著將至今的謊言吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.58,0:25:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.25,0:25:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.45,0:25:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我陶醉故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.82,0:25:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我行不通…woo
